statements: SELECT * FROM 3d_printing_machine_utilization;
SELECT machine_id, utilization_rate FROM 3d_printing_machine_utilization WHERE material_used = 'PLA';
SELECT printing_time, material_used FROM 3d_printing_machine_utilization ORDER BY printing_time DESC;
SELECT AVG(utilization_rate) FROM 3d_printing_machine_utilization;
SELECT * FROM 3d_printing_machine_utilization WHERE utilization_rate > 0.8;
SELECT * FROM 3d_printing_machine_utilization ORDER BY printing_time DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT machine_id, AVG(utilization_rate) AS avg_rate FROM 3d_printing_machine_utilization GROUP BY machine_id
SELECT * FROM 3d_printing_machine_utilization WHERE material_used LIKE '%PLA%'
SELECT MAX(utilization_rate) AS max_rate, MIN(utilization_rate) AS min_rate FROM 3d_printing_machine_utilization
SELECT machine_id, COUNT(*) AS total_records FROM 3d_printing_machine_utilization GROUP BY machine_id ORDER BY total_records DESC
SELECT * FROM 3d_printing_jobs WHERE job_status = 'completed';
SELECT job_id, machine_id, material_used FROM 3d_printing_jobs WHERE start_time >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT job_id, start_time, end_time FROM 3d_printing_jobs WHERE machine_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT machine_id, manufacturer, model FROM machine_details WHERE purchase_date < '2021-01-01';
SELECT job_id, job_status FROM 3d_printing_jobs WHERE material_used = 'PLA';
SELECT * FROM 3d_printing_jobs WHERE job_status='Completed';
SELECT job_id, start_time, material_used FROM 3d_printing_jobs WHERE material_used='PLA' ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT machine_id, manufacturer FROM machine_details WHERE purchase_date > '2021-01-01';
SELECT job_id, start_time, end_time FROM 3d_printing_jobs WHERE job_status='InProgress' ORDER BY end_time ASC;
SELECT machine_id, model, purchase_date FROM machine_details WHERE manufacturer='Prusa' ORDER BY purchase_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM 3d_printing_machine;
SELECT model, manufacturer FROM 3d_printing_machine;
SELECT machine_id, location, manufacturer FROM 3d_printing_machine WHERE manufacturer = 'Xprinter';
SELECT job_id, start_time, end_time, quantity FROM print_job WHERE quantity > 10;
SELECT operator_id, name, skill_level FROM operator WHERE skill_level = 'Expert';
SELECT * FROM 3d_printing_machine
SELECT machine_id, location, manufacturer FROM 3d_printing_machine ORDER BY manufacturer DESC
SELECT * FROM print_job WHERE quantity > 10 AND material = 'PLA'
SELECT operator_id, name, skill_level FROM operator ORDER BY operator_id LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM 3d_printing_machine WHERE location LIKE '%City%'
SELECT * FROM 3d_printing_jobs;
SELECT printer_id, job_type, material_type FROM 3d_printing_jobs ORDER BY printer_id DESC;
SELECT job_id, job_start_time, job_end_time FROM 3d_printing_jobs WHERE job_start_time >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT printer_model, printer_location FROM printers WHERE printer_location = 'Office';
SELECT material_id, material_name, material_cost FROM materials ORDER BY material_cost ASC;
SELECT * FROM 3d_printing_jobs WHERE job_type = 'Prototyping' ORDER BY job_start_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT job_id, job_type, material_type, job_start_time FROM 3d_printing_jobs WHERE material_type = 'PLA' AND job_start_time > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY job_start_time ASC;

SELECT p.printer_model, j.job_type, j.job_start_time, j.job_end_time FROM printers p INNER JOIN 3d_printing_jobs j ON p.printer_id = j.printer_id WHERE p.printer_location = 'Lab A' ORDER BY j.job_end_time DESC LIMIT 3;

SELECT m.material_name, m.material_cost, j.job_type, j.job_start_time, j.job_end_time FROM materials m INNER JOIN 3d_printing_jobs j ON m.material_type = j.material_type ORDER BY m.material_cost DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT m.material_name, COUNT(j.job_id) AS total_jobs FROM materials m LEFT JOIN 3d_printing_jobs j ON m.material_type = j.material_type GROUP BY m.material_name ORDER BY total_jobs DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM UtilizationMetrics;
SELECT machine_id, utilization_percentage FROM UtilizationMetrics WHERE utilization_percentage > 80;
SELECT machine_name, manufacturer, location FROM MachineDetails WHERE manufacturer = 'HP';
SELECT * FROM MaintenanceLogs ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC;
SELECT user_id, username, email, role FROM UserProfiles WHERE role = 'Admin';
SELECT * FROM UtilizationMetrics WHERE utilization_percentage > 80 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT DISTINCT machine_id, AVG(utilization_percentage) AS average_utilization FROM UtilizationMetrics GROUP BY machine_id HAVING COUNT(id) > 5 ORDER BY average_utilization DESC;
SELECT machine_name, manufacturer, location FROM MachineDetails WHERE machine_id IN (SELECT machine_id FROM UtilizationMetrics WHERE utilization_percentage < 20);
SELECT job_name, job_duration, filament_used FROM PrintJobLogs WHERE filament_used > 100 ORDER BY job_duration DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT user_id, username, email, role FROM UserProfiles WHERE role = 'admin' OR role = 'manager';
